nodes.text: Tseyla was a a Mirialan female Jedi Master of the Jedi Order. During the Cold War between the Galactic Republic and the reconstituted Sith Empire she was stationed on Coruscant where she served as a Jedi Consular and combat instructor.
Tseyla appears only in the game files for Star Wars: The Old Republic as her character was cut from the game. Tseyla's file can be found on Jedipedia.
